 <refnamediv>
  <refname>basename</refname>
  <refpurpose>dosya isimlerinden dizin ve soneki ayırır</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>
 <refsynopsisdiv>
  <synopsis format="linespecific"><command>basename </command><emphasis>isim </emphasis>[<emphasis>sonek</emphasis>]
<command>basename </command><emphasis>seçenekler</emphasis></synopsis>
 </refsynopsisdiv>
 <refsection>
  <info>
   <title>AÇIKLAMA</title>
  </info>
  <para>
Dizin bileşenlerini silerek <varname>isim</varname>'i basar. Şayet belirtilmişse, dosya <varname>sonek</varname>ini de kaldırır.
    </para>
  <para>
   <glosslist>
    <glossentry>
     <glossterm>
      <command>--help</command>
     </glossterm>
     <glossdef>
      <para>Bu yardım metnini basar ve çıkar.
        </para>
     </glossdef>
    </glossentry>
    <glossentry>
     <glossterm>
      <command>--version</command>
     </glossterm>
     <glossdef>
      <para>Sürüm bilgilerini basar ve çıkar.
        </para>
     </glossdef>
    </glossentry>
   </glosslist>
  </para>
 </refsection>
 <refsection>
  <info>
   <title>ÖRNEKLER</title>
  </info>
  <para>
   <glosslist>
    <glossentry>
     <glossterm>
      <command>basename /usr/bin/sort</command>
     </glossterm>
     <glossdef>
      <para>"sort" çıktılanır.</para>
     </glossdef>
    </glossentry>
    <glossentry>
     <glossterm>
      <command>basename include/stdio.h .h</command>
     </glossterm>
     <glossdef>
      <para>"stdio" çıktılanır.</para>
     </glossdef>
    </glossentry>
   </glosslist>
  </para>
 </refsection>
 <refsection>
  <info>
   <title>YAZAN</title>
  </info>
  <para>
Bilinmiyor.
    </para>
 </refsection>
